Para fluxo laminar:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{dp_{f}}{dL}=\frac{K\bar{v}^{n}\left(\frac{3+\frac{1}{n}}{0.0416}\right)^{n}}{144000d^{1+n}}
